title: I MUST KEEP GOING
itunes:title: I MUST KEEP GOING
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
There is someone in their grave today, who would do anything for what you have. Your viewpoint, your PERSPECTIVE is everything! You don't get what you should have, you get what you MUST have. One of the Best Motivational Speeches Ever featuring Marcus Elevation Taylor (https://bit.ly/MarcusTaylorMotiversity).


Music by Secession Studios (https://bit.ly/SecessionStudiosYouTube).
